  2→ * Milestone 3: DPoP + RAR Verification at Brain Resource Server
  3→ *
  4→ * Traces: US-005 (DPoP Proof Verification), US-006 (RAR Operation Scope Verification)
  5→ *
  6→ * Verifies:
  7→ * - Brain rejects Bearer tokens with 401 "dpop_required"
  8→ * - Brain rejects session cookies with 401 "dpop_required"
  9→ * - DPoP proof validated: structure, signature, claims
 10→ * - JWK thumbprint matched against cnf.jkt
 11→ * - Nonce cache rejects reused jti
 12→ * - Clock skew tolerance (60s past, 5s future)
 13→ * - Type must be "brain_action"
 14→ * - Action and resource matched exactly
 15→ * - Constraint bounds enforced
 16→ * - Specific error codes returned
 17→ * - Same pipeline for agent and human tokens
 18→ *
 19→ * Driving ports:
 20→ *   POST /api/mcp/:ws/*  (DPoP-protected Brain endpoints)
 21→ */
